location.fullValue: Milton Plan, Pepperwood Crossing | OLO Builders

data.description: This single story home is in a prime location, is well maintained and move in ready – what more could you ask for! This property is located off County Line Road and is near Idaho Falls, Rigby and Rexburg. Additionally, there is only one neighbor and an open field on the other! Inside the home is open and bright – creating a very welcoming environment for all who enter. Throughout the home is Luxury Vinyl Plank making the maintenance and cleaning so easy. The living room, dining area and kitchen are all open to each other making entertaining fun for all. Unique light fixtures in the dining and kitchen add such a great touch to the home. The kitchen is a large U-shape with mounds of cabinet space and countertop area. The exterior is fully fenced with a paving stone area to create the perfect outdoor escape. Come take a look!
